OL,3,CPopular literary festival cancelled
OL,4,Cdue to 'spiralling costs'
OL,6,FThe Alderney Literary Festival has
OL,7,Fbeen cancelled this year, with
OL,8,Forganisers blaming financial pressures
OL,9,Fand "travel uncertainty".
OL,11,FThe event's organiser, Alderney
OL,12,FLiterary Trust, shared the news on
OL,13,Fsocial media with a statement, which
OL,14,Fcalled it a "difficult decision".
OL,16,FThe festival usually takes place every
OL,17,FMarch in the historic Island Hall, and
OL,18,Fhas been running every year since
OL,19,F2014, except during the Covid lockdown
OL,20,Fin 2021.
