OL,4,Cdue to 'spiralling costs'
OL,6,FIsabel Picornell, the festival's
OL,7,Ffounder, said: "The problem is we have
OL,8,Freached the stage where it is not
OL,9,Fpossible to get the guest authors and
OL,10,Fprofessional support staff, as well as
OL,11,Four regular festivalgoers."
OL,13,FMs Picornell added that 80% of those
OL,14,Fvisiting the festival come from
OL,15,Foutside the island.
OL,17,F"We have many world-renowned authors
OL,18,Fwanting to come to Alderney, along
OL,19,Fwith regular visitors from overseas,
OL,20,Fincluding Guernsey and Jersey, so this
OL,21,Fnews will disappoint a lot of people."
