OL,6,FThe Trust attracts an array of
OL,7,Faccomplished authors to its events,
OL,8,Fhaving previously featured
OL,9,Finternational bestselling author
OL,10,FAnthony Horowitz at the Young People
OL,11,FLiterary Festival 2019 at St Anne's
OL,12,FSchool, Alderney.
OL,14,FAccording to its website, the festival
OL,15,Fdeliberately keeps its size small to
OL,16,Fcreate an intimate environment for
OL,17,Fvisitors.
