OL,6,FHowever, the Trust has now warned that
OL,7,Funless the future of the island's
OL,8,Frunway is resolved soon, the 2027
OL,9,Ffestival could suffer the same fate.
OL,11,F"Traditionally, the festival has been
OL,12,Fdeliberately scheduled for the
OL,13,Fshoulder months to bring people to
OL,14,FAlderney when there are fewer
OL,15,Ftourists," Ms Picornell stated.
OL,16,F"However, flight frequency is reduced
OL,17,Fduring those months."
