OL,6,FThere has been frustration among
OL,7,FAlderney residents and politicians
OL,8,Fover the deteriorating runway that is
OL,9,Fcurrently covered with a patchwork of
OL,10,Ftemporary repairs.
OL,12,FGuernsey's Committee for Policy and
OL,13,FResources (P&R) wants new proposals to
OL,14,Fwiden the runway debated in the States
OL,15,Fin February, with the hopes of
OL,16,Fstarting the work in early 2027.
OL,18,FHowever, Alderney Airport may need to
OL,19,Fclose for an extended period of time
OL,20,Fwhile the work is completed.
