OL,3,CPopular literary festival cancelled
OL,4,Cdue to 'spiralling costs'
OL,6,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez, President
OL,7,Fof P&R, told ITV News: "It's essential
OL,8,Ffor Alderney to have an operational
OL,9,Frunway, and it really is as simple as
OL,10,Fthat.
OL,12,F"We have committed to bringing in this
OL,13,Fproject at the lowest possible cost
OL,14,Fwithout cutting corners on things like
OL,15,Fsafety or regulatory standards.
OL,17,F"At the end of the day, infrastructure
OL,18,Fprojects like these are inherently
OL,19,Fexpensive, but they also need to be
OL,20,Fdone."
